__e: -search Add a dash (-) or NOT before a word to exclude from search. Note that NOT acts as a filtering operator so you cannot have a search containing only NOT operators. You cannot combine OR with NOT ( john OR NOT bill is not valid)
In Italian, it's to be or not to be. That is the question.
